a6 xb7 h2e y172e ff6 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we </div><div class="t m275c x16 h2b y560 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">look about us to see what we can</div><div class="t mb0f xaf h2b yba8 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">. </div><div class="t m2058 x2b h2b y163b ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> do to reciprocate the </div><div class="t m1ef7 xb7 h2b y19fa ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">favor. The greater the gift bestowed, the greater the sense </div><div class="t m235f x0 h2b y1778 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of obligation and gratitude. If the trifling favors hesto we </div><div class="t m2abf xb7 h2b y180d ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">upon man by their fellows can call forth a return of &quot;gifts&quot; </div><div class="t m240f xb7 h2b y205 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">according to the receiver&apos;s ability, how much more should the </div><div class="t m2323 xb7 h2b yb65 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;gift&quot; of </div><div class="t mf2c xc h2e yb65 ff6 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lire </div><div class="t m1014 x3f h2b yb65 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and </div><div class="t m843 x6c h2e y384 ff6 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">redemption </div><div class="t m2bcd x68 h2b yb68 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">call forth from man constant </div><div class="t mb88 x29 h2e y190b ff6 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The needs of the cause of God arc world-wide. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
